| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2071 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 09563384-5796-5e4c-8d6e-3d8c97f1f3ac"
